data.description: 2300+ SF move-in-ready 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath tri-level home on 3/4 acre inviting lot with mature trees in quiet neighborhood and desirable school district (Prairie Hill, Willowbrook, Hononegah). New Roof, Gutters and Skylights Aug 2023. Professional new paint throughout over Kal-Kote plaster. Spacious kitchen with new Quartz countertops and updated stainless appliances. Large family room off back of home with skylights & gas fireplace. Direct access to freshly reconditioned deck, Large shed with new matching roof, overhead garage door and loft offers plenty of storage space and includes riding lawn mower with asking price + sale. Attached 2-Car garage with attic and stairway access to additional 565 SF basement & utility room, also accessible from home. Modernized features include lighting, shelving, vanities, vanity tops, bathroom fixtures, etc. High quality LVP flooring installed in 2019 throughout Well & Septic.
